Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:00.93,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}面具藏起真容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:06.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,200)}是遥远过去的绝望
